### ================================================================
### STEP 3. OTA 예약 생성
### 실행 순서: hotel.http → room_type.http → 여기
### ================================================================

### [야놀자] 예약 생성 (2박)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YANOLJA",
  "otaReservationId": "YANOLJA-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "홍길동",
  "guestPhone": "010-1234-5678",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-03",
  "totalPrice": 200000
}

###

### [여기어때] 예약 생성 (1박)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YEOGI",
  "otaReservationId": "YEOGI-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "김철수",
  "guestPhone": "010-9876-5432",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-02",
  "totalPrice": 100000
}

###

### [요기서] 예약 생성 (2박)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YOGISEO",
  "otaReservationId": "YOGISEO-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "이영희",
  "guestPhone": "010-1111-2222",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-02",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-04",
  "totalPrice": 200000
}

###

### ================================================================
### STEP 4. OTA 예약 확정 (PENDING → CONFIRMED)
### ================================================================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations/YANOLJA-RES-001/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ================================================================
### STEP 5. OTA 예약 수정 (날짜/금액 변경)
### 확정 전(PENDING) or 확정 후(CONFIRMED) 모두 가능
### ================================================================

PUT http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations/YANOLJA-RES-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-05",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-07",
  "totalPrice": 250000
}

###

### ================================================================
### STEP 6. OTA 예약 취소 (재고 자동 원복)
### ================================================================

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations/YANOLJA-RES-001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ================================================================
### 멱등성 테스트 - 중복 요청 (DUPLICATE_RESERVATION 에러 확인)
### ================================================================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YANOLJA",
  "otaReservationId": "YANOLJA-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "홍길동",
  "guestPhone": "010-1234-5678",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-03",
  "totalPrice": 200000
}
